OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1778785872
OL,3,CHampshire and Thames Valley police
OL,4,Ctrial world's first laughing gas
OL,5,Cbreathalyser
OL,7,FThe world's first roadside laughing
OL,8,Fgas breathalyser is being trialled by
OL,9,Ftwo police forces in the south of
OL,10,FEngland.
OL,12,FHampshire and Isle of Wight
OL,13,FConstabulary and Thames Valley Police
OL,14,Fare testing the device for what they
OL,15,Fdescribe as the "emerging threat" of
OL,16,Fdrivers taking to their vehicles while
OL,17,Fhigh on nitrous oxide - referred to as
OL,18,FNOS and also known as "hippy crack".
OL,26,@wD@QOUwD@aO]zD@WOUzD@cO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
