OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1778785872
OL,3,CHampshire and Thames Valley police
OL,4,Ctrial world's first laughing gas
OL,5,Cbreathalyser
OL,7,F"Nitrous oxide is a growing issue,
OL,8,Fespecially with young drivers who
OL,9,Fdon't understand the harm it can
OL,10,Fcause, so when we saw the opportunity
OL,11,Fto test this new technology, we knew
OL,12,Fhow important it could be towards
OL,13,Fthese devices being rolled out across
OL,14,Fthe country."
OL,16,FIn 2023, three teenagers, Elliot
OL,17,FPullen, 17, and 18-year-olds Ethan
OL,18,FGoddard and Daniel Hancock died when
OL,19,Fthe car they were passengers in
OL,20,Fcrashed into a tree alongside the A415
OL,21,Fin Marcham, Oxfordshire.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@MO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
