OL,4,Ctrial world's first laughing gas
OL,5,Cbreathalyser
OL,7,FThe 18-year-old driver, Thomas
OL,8,FJohnson, was filmed inhaling laughing
OL,9,Fgas behind the wheel just moments
OL,10,Fbefore the crash and was driving at
OL,11,Fspeeds of up to 100mph.
